title: DESIGNER FURNISHED STUNNING CONDO BRICKELL FLATIRON!!!
posting_body: ['Designer furnished rental available in the most sought after building… Brickell Flatiron.', 'Enjoy an oversized balcony with bay and city views.', 'This spacious one bed, one and half bath condo is ready for immediate move in.', 'Full-service building attendants with 24/7 security, 24-hour valet service, secured and covered designated self-parking garage, charging stations for electric vehicles, bicycle storage, 6 destination-controlled and extra high-speed elevators.', 'Rooftop pool with expansive views of the Brickell skyline including 360º of fully unobstructed gorgeous water and city views.', 'Exclusive rooftop spa & fitness center featuring pilates, yoga and aerobics studios, private steam and sauna rooms and locker facilities, lap pool on the 18th floor and much more.', 'all units are one year lease min!', 'credit score close to 700 or higher required, proof of income 2,5 greater than rent price, first month + last month + security deposit to move in!', 'Dilya Taveras', 'Equity Realty', 'TEXT :', 'show contact info']
